New Homes for Sale






























LGI Homes has set the pace for excellence in affordable home building, garnering praise for an efficient business model that saves buyers money, and winning awards for the unmatched quality of its homes.
Our homes are built on-site, with thoughtfully designed floor plans that include all of the details that are important to your family: quality appliances, custom cabinetry, dual-car garages, landscaped yards, and more. This attention to customer needs, along with our consistent individualized service, has proven so popular that from our humble beginnings in markets throughout Texas, we've now been able to expand our success to the beautiful metropolises of Phoenix, Arizona; Tucson, Arizona; Albuquerque, New Mexico; Denver, Colorado; Atlanta, Georgia; Athens, Georgia; Charlotte, North Carolina; Raleigh, North Carolina; Winston-Salem, North Carolina; Nashville, Tennessee; Tampa, Florida; Lakeland, Florida; Orlando, Florida; Fort Myers, Florida; Jacksonville, Florida; Minneapolis, Minnesota; Olympia, Washington; Tacoma, Washington; Seattle, Washington and Portland, Oregon.
In fact, since 2003 LGI Homes has become one of the fastest growing homebuilders in the nation, driven by our commitment to our customers, and our desire to make dreams of homeownership come true. We have crafted beautiful yet affordable homes, simplified the buying process, and stood by our clients every step of the way; and in turn our homeowners' praise has garnered us awards in customer satisfaction, and pushed us to constantly better our product, our service, and our business. There are many factors that separate LGI Homes from other Arizona, Texas, New Mexico, Colorado, Georgia, Florida, North Carolina, Tennessee, Washington and Oregon homebuilders, but outstanding quality and customer service is what sets us apart. 
Why not browse through our communities and find the home that's right for you? We guarantee you'll find something to love.



